sequenceDiagram
    participant P as Probe
    participant R as Runner
    participant B as Disk Buffer
    participant X as Exporter
    participant Pr as Prometheus
    participant L as Loki
    P->>R: ProbeResult
    R->>B: write (NDJSON, fsync/64)
    R->>X: record_probe (metrics)
    Pr->>X: scrape :9101/metrics
    R->>L: ship structured log
    Note over B: drained + acked on delivery;<br/>survives restart
